<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dog Fun — Pagina non trovata</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: #fdf6ec;
            color: #3d2b1f;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .dog-sad {
            font-size: 8rem;
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            animation: wobble 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes wobble {
            0%, 100% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            25% { transform: rotate(-5deg); }
            75% { transform: rotate(5deg); }
        }

        .error-code {
            font-size: 6rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #e8a020;
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: .5rem;
        }

        .error-message {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            max-width: 500px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #6b5544;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .paw-prints {
            color: #d4a574;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            letter-spacing: .5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .btn-home {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #e8a020;
            color: white;
            padding: .9rem 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background .2s, transform .2s;
        }

        .btn-home:hover {
            background: #c4871a;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="dog-sad">&#128021;</div>
    <div class="error-code">404</div>
    <div class="paw-prints">&#128062; &#128062; &#128062; &#128062; &#128062;</div>
    <p class="error-message">
        Mi spiace, ho scavato a fondo ma non ho trovato quello che stai cercando!
    </p>
    <a href="/" class="btn-home">Torna alla Home</a>
</body>
</html>
